  ('Jacqui Duncan', 'General Manager, NSW', 'General Manager | Emerging Tech Startups | CEMS Alumna · Driving the growth of Australia’s largest innovation community.I’m a business leader with experience in international trade, tech, and startups, driving growth and innovation across the country’s business and tech ecosystem.At Stone & Chalk Group, I lead the NSW business, running the front door to the state’s innovation sector through our Tech Central Innovation Hub - part of Australia’s newest precinct backed by $38.5 million in government investment. The 8,000SQM hub is home to 1,000+ founde', 'Sydney, New South Wales, Australia', 'Senior operator with extensive ANZ market experience.', ARRAY['Active Advisor', 'Startup Advisor'], 'https://linkedin.com/in/jacqui-duncan', NULL, NULL, 'Stone & Chalk', FALSE, '[{"name": "Stone & Chalk"}, {"name": "IdeaFloat"}]'::jsonb, 'usa', ARRAY['usa', 'australia'], NULL, 'jacqui-duncan', 'Active Advisor', ARRAY['international_entrant'], TRUE, FALSE),
