  ('Bradley Gilbert', 'Founder & CEO', 'Founder & CEO at Traders4Traders · Brad is the Director & Founder of Traders4Traders, a Forex trading education company. T4T has a specialised training program designed to produce high performance FX traders, of which the best of the best are recruited into the T4T trading team.He is a registered Commodity Trading Advisor with the NFA (USA) and is licensed by ASIC to Manage Forex Discretionary accounts for wholesale clients. Brad has been a professional Forex Trader since 1990, having worked for Citibank (Sydney, London, New York', 'Greater Sydney Area', 'Senior operator with extensive ANZ market experience.', ARRAY['International Founder', 'Fintech Founder', 'Cross-border'], 'https://linkedin.com/in/bradley-gilbert-63755b23', NULL, NULL, 'Traders4Traders', FALSE, '[{"name": "Traders4Traders"}, {"name": "Traders GCF LLC - Commodity Trading Advisor (0464419)"}]'::jsonb, 'ireland', ARRAY['ireland', 'australia'], NULL, 'bradley-gilbert', 'International Founder', ARRAY['international_entrant'], TRUE, FALSE)
